es the\nbackscattering efficiency for some configurations. For other configurations,\nthe backscattering efficiency has an undulating behavior with increase in\nelectrical size, and is highly affected by the shape and the constitutive\nanisotropy of the ellipsoid.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Mar 2019 19:19:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-03-22"}
